Overturned Vehicle in Two Vehicle Collision at Drury Ave & Independence Ave, Kansas City, Missouri, 64123

12/1/2022, 4:43:59 PM

Firefighters and EMS personnel have received a 911 report of a vehicle collision with possible injuries.

12/1/2022, 4:36:31 PM

First responders on the scene advised that the collision involved two vehicles. They further advised that one of the vehicles has overturned.

12/1/2022, 4:43:18 PM

This incident occurred in city council district 3. 

Representative: Melissa Robinson @Robinson4kc and Brandon Ellington @ellington_b at-large
